(1) Open the project with Android-Studio

(2) Refer to following guide for background activity launch
   https://developer.android.com/guide/components/activities/background-starts
   
(3) In this example, it used SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW permission.
    To test it, do followings to avoid permission removal after reboot.
      Settings -> System -> Developer options:
        Verify apps over USB : set false

